Program: Discovery
Title: Science and a look ahead
Link: https://www.bbc.co.uk/programmes/p03jrwl4
Last Broadcast Date: 08 January 1996
What the year ahead might bring in science. What might science help discover in 1996, a speculative look ahead. Also in the programme how does the body know when it's hungry, how does it deal with sugar and a future TV technology. Presenter: Martin Redfern.